@host = http://localhost:11434

### Version (must report >= 0.6.4)
GET {{host}}/api/version

### List models (from the claude CLI)
GET {{host}}/api/tags

### Show a model's capabilities
POST {{host}}/api/show
Content-Type: application/json

{ "model": "claude-sonnet-4-5" }

### OpenAI chat (Ask mode) — streamed SSE
POST {{host}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-5",
  "stream": true,
  "messages": [ { "role": "user", "content": "Say hi in exactly three words." } ]
}

### Native Ollama chat (NDJSON)
POST {{host}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "claude-sonnet-4-5",
  "stream": true,
  "messages": [ { "role": "user", "content": "Say hi in exactly three words." } ]
}
